\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-1 mb-4\" data-kid=\"146\">\n            <i class=\"ti ti-star-filled text-sm\" style=\"color:#FFD700;\" data-kid=\"147\"></i>\n            <i class=\"ti ti-star-filled text-sm\" style=\"color:#FFD700;\" data-kid=\"148\"></i>\n            <i class=\"ti ti-star-filled text-sm\" style=\"color:#FFD700;\" data-kid=\"149\"></i>\n            <i class=\"ti ti-star-filled text-sm\" style=\"color:#FFD700;\" data-kid=\"150\"></i>\n            <i class=\"ti ti-star-filled text-sm\" style=\"color:#FFD700;\" data-kid=\"151\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"text-white/70 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6\" data-kid=\"152\">\"I've been trading on EthioSwap for 6 months. The escrow system is flawless — I've never lost a single trade. Best P2P platform in Ethiopia!\"</p>\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"153\">\n            <img src=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/40?u=biruk-addis\" alt=\"Biruk A.\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-kid=\"154\">\n            <div data-kid=\"155\">\n              <div class=\"font-semibold text-sm\" data-kid=\"156\">Biruk Addis</div>\n              <div class=\"text-xs text-white/40\" data-kid=\"157\">Gold Trader · 340 trades</div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"testimonial-card p-7 rounded-3xl border backdrop-blur-sm\" style=\"background:rgba(13,21,32,0.8);border-color:rgba(0,212,160,0.2);\" data-kid=\"158\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-1 mb-4\" data-kid=\"159\">\n            <i class=\"ti ti-star-filled text-sm\" style=\"color:#FFD700;\" data-kid=\"160\"></i>\n            <i class=\"ti ti-star-filled text-sm\" style=\"color:#FFD700;\" data-kid=\"161\"></i>\n            <i class=\"ti ti-star-filled text-sm\" style=\"color:#FFD700;\" data-kid=\"162\"></i>\n            <i class=\"ti ti-star-filled text-sm\" style=\"color:#FFD700;\" data-kid=\"163\"></i>\n            <i class=\"ti ti-star-filled text-sm\" style=\"color:#FFD700;\" data-kid=\"164\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"text-white/70 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6\" data-kid=\"165\">\"Sending money via Telebirr and getting ETH instantly is amazing. The process is smooth and the support team is very responsive.\"</p>\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"166\">\n            <img src=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/40?u=senait-haile\" alt=\"Senait H.\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-kid=\"167\">\n            <div data-kid=\"168\">\n              <div class=\"font-semibold text-sm\" data-kid=\"169\">Senait Haile</div>\n              <div class=\"text-xs text-white/40\" data-kid=\"170\">Verified Trader · 128 trades</div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"testimonial-card p-7 rounded-3xl border backdrop-blur-sm\" style=\"background:rgba(13,21,32,0.8);border-color:rgba(255,215,0,0.15);\" data-kid=\"171\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-1 mb-4\" data-kid=\"172\">\n            <i class=\"ti ti-star-filled text-sm\" style=\"color:#FFD700;\" data-kid=\"173\"></i>\n            <i class=\"ti ti-star-filled text-sm\" style=\"color:#FFD700;\" data-kid=\"174\"></i>\n            <i class=\"ti ti-star-filled text-sm\" style=\"color:#FFD700;\" data-kid=\"175\"></i>\n            <i class=\"ti ti-star-filled text-sm\" style=\"color:#FFD700;\" data-kid=\"176\"></i>\n            <i class=\"ti ti-star-half-filled text-sm\" style=\"color:#FFD700;\" data-kid=\"177\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"text-white/70 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6\" data-kid=\"178\">\"The KYC process was fast and the platform is very secure. I recommend EthioSwap to everyone who wants to safely trade crypto in Ethiopia.\"</p>\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"179\">\n            <img src=\"https://i.pravatar.cc/40?u=dawit-bekele\" alt=\"Dawit B.\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-kid=\"180\">\n            <div data-kid=\"181\">\n              <div class=\"font-semibold text-sm\" data-kid=\"182\">Dawit Bekele</div>\n              <div class=\"text-xs text-white/40\" data-kid=\"183\">Silver Trader · 87 trades</div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section class=\"py-24\" style=\"background:rgba(0,12,22,0.6);\" data-kid=\"184\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-[860px] mx-auto px-8\" data-kid=\"185\">\n      <div class=\"text-center mb-16\" data-kid=\"186\">\n        <div class=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-3\" style=\"color:#FFD700;\" data-kid=\"187\">FAQ</div>\n        <h2 class=\"text-4xl font-bold\" style=\"font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;\" data-kid=\"188\">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"space-y-3\" data-kid=\"189\">\n        \n        <div class=\"faq-item rounded-2xl border overflow-hidden\" style=\"background:#0d1520;border-color:rgba(255,215,0,0.15);\" data-kid=\"190\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between p-5 cursor-pointer\" data-kid=\"191\">\n            <span class=\"font-semibold\" data-kid=\"192\">How does the escrow system protect me?</span>\n            <i class=\"ti ti-chevron-down text-lg\" style=\"color:#FFD700;\" data-kid=\"193\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"px-5 pb-5 text-white/55 text-sm leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"194\">When a trade starts, the seller's ETH is locked in our escrow smart contract. The crypto is only released to the buyer after the seller confirms receipt of payment — this eliminates all fraud risk.</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"faq-item rounded-2xl border overflow-hidden\" style=\"background:#0d1520;border-color:rgba(0,212,160,0.12);\" data-kid=\"195\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between p-5 cursor-pointer\" data-kid=\"196\">\n            <span class=\"font-semibold\" data-kid=\"197\">What payment methods are supported?</span>\n            <i class=\"ti ti-chevron-down text-lg\" style=\"color:#00d4a0;\" data-kid=\"198\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"px-5 pb-5 text-white/55 text-sm leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"199\">We support Telebirr, CBE (Commercial Bank of Ethiopia), Awash Bank, Amhara Bank, Oromia Bank, and other major Ethiopian banks.</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"faq-item rounded-2xl border overflow-hidden\" style=\"background:#0d1520;border-color:rgba(255,215,0,0.15);\" data-kid=\"200\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between p-5 cursor-pointer\" data-kid=\"201\">\n            <span class=\"font-semibold\" data-kid=\"202\">How long does KYC verification take?</span>\n            <i class=\"ti ti-chevron-down text-lg\" style=\"color:#FFD700;\" data-kid=\"203\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"px-5 pb-5 text-white/55 text-sm leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"204\">Most KYC verifications are completed within 2-4 hours during business hours. You'll need a valid national ID and a selfie.</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"faq-item rounded-2xl border overflow-hidden\" style=\"background:#0d1520;border-color:rgba(0,212,160,0.12);\" data-kid=\"205\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between p-5 cursor-pointer\" data-kid=\"206\">\n            <span class=\"font-semibold\" data-kid=\"207\">What are the trading fees?</span>\n            <i class=\"ti ti-chevron-down text-lg\" style=\"color:#00d4a0;\" data-kid=\"208\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"px-5 pb-5 text-white/55 text-sm leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"209\">EthioSwap charges a flat 0.5% fee on completed trades, one of the lowest rates in the market. There are no hidden fees.</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"faq-item rounded-2xl border overflow-hidden\" style=\"background:#0d1520;border-color:rgba(255,215,0,0.15);\" data-kid=\"210\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between p-5 cursor-pointer\" data-kid=\"211\">\n            <span class=\"font-semibold\" data-kid=\"212\">What happens if there's a dispute?</span>\n            <i class=\"ti ti-chevron-down text-lg\" style=\"color:#FFD700;\" data-kid=\"213\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"px-5 pb-5 text-white/55 text-sm leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"214\">Our dispute resolution team reviews all evidence submitted by both parties and makes a fair decision within 24 hours. The escrowed funds are held safely until resolution.</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <section class=\"py-20 relative overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"215\">\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#004953,#001a20,#004953);\" data-kid=\"216\"></div>\n    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-10\" style=\"background-image:radial-gradient(#FFD700 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:30px 30px;\" data-kid=\"217\"></div>\n    <div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-[860px] mx-auto px-8 text-center\" data-kid=\"218\">\n      <h2 class=\"text-5xl font-extrabold mb-4\" style=\"font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;\" data-kid=\"219\">Ready to Start Trading?</h2>\n      <p class=\"text-white/60 text-lg mb-8\" data-kid=\"220\">Join 12,400+ Ethiopians already trading crypto securely on EthioSwap.</p>\n      <div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 justify-center\" data-kid=\"221\">\n        <button class=\"px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-base\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FFD700,#FFA500);color:#010B13;\" data-kid=\"222\">Create Free Account</button>\n        <button class=\"px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-base border\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);color:white;\" data-kid=\"223\">Explore Markets</button>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  \n  <footer class=\"py-14 border-t\" style=\"background:#010B13;border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);\" data-kid=\"224\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-8\" data-kid=\"225\">\n      <div class=\"grid grid-cols-4 gap-10 mb-12\" data-kid=\"226\">\n        <div data-kid=\"227\">\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\" data-kid=\"228\">\n            <div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FFD700,#FFA500);\" data-kid=\"229\">\n              <i class=\"ti ti-shield-check text-[#010B13] text-sm\" data-kid=\"230\"></i>\n            </div>\n            <span class=\"text-lg font-bold\" style=\"font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;color:#FFD700;\" data-kid=\"231\">EthioSwap</span>\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"232\">Ethiopia's most secure P2P crypto escrow trading platform.</p>\n          <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mt-5\" data-kid=\"233\">\n            <div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center border cursor-pointer hover:border-[#FFD700]\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\" data-kid=\"234\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-telegram text-white/60 text-lg\" data-kid=\"235\"></i></div>\n            <div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center border cursor-pointer hover:border-[#FFD700]\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\" data-kid=\"236\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-whatsapp text-white/60 text-lg\" data-kid=\"237\"></i></div>\n            <div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center border cursor-pointer hover:border-[#FFD700]\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\" data-kid=\"238\"><i class=\"ti ti-brand-twitter text-white/60 text-lg\" data-kid=\"239\"></i></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div data-kid=\"240\">\n          <h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-4 text-sm\" style=\"font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;\" data-kid=\"241\">Platform</h4>\n          <ul class=\"space-y-2.5 text-sm text-white/50\" data-kid=\"242\">\n            <li data-kid=\"243\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white\" data-kid=\"244\">P2P Marketplace</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"245\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white\" data-kid=\"246\">Trade History</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"247\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white\" data-kid=\"248\">Escrow System</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"249\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white\" data-kid=\"250\">API Docs</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n        <div data-kid=\"251\">\n          <h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-4 text-sm\" style=\"font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;\" data-kid=\"252\">Support</h4>\n          <ul class=\"space-y-2.5 text-sm text-white/50\" data-kid=\"253\">\n            <li data-kid=\"254\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white\" data-kid=\"255\">Help Center</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"256\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white\" data-kid=\"257\">Contact Us</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"258\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white\" data-kid=\"259\">Dispute Resolution</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"260\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white\" data-kid=\"261\">Report Issue</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n        <div data-kid=\"262\">\n          <h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-4 text-sm\" style=\"font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;\" data-kid=\"263\">Legal</h4>\n          <ul class=\"space-y-2.5 text-sm text-white/50\" data-kid=\"264\">\n            <li data-kid=\"265\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white\" data-kid=\"266\">Terms of Service</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"267\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white\" data-kid=\"268\">Privacy Policy</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"269\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white\" data-kid=\"270\">KYC Policy</a></li>\n            <li data-kid=\"271\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white\" data-kid=\"272\">Cookie Policy</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"pt-8 border-t flex items-center justify-between\" style=\"border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);\" data-kid=\"273\">\n        <div class=\"text-white/30 text-sm\" data-kid=\"274\">© 2025 EthioSwap. All rights reserved.</div>\n        <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-white/30 text-sm\" data-kid=\"275\">\n          <i class=\"ti ti-shield-check text-xs\" style=\"color:#00d4a0;\" data-kid=\"276\"></i> Secured by Smart Escrow Technology\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </footer>\n</div>\n\n\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3/dist/gsap.min.js\" data-kid=\"277\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3/dist/ScrollTrigger.min.js\" data-kid=\"278\"></script>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://unpkg.com/lenis@1/dist/lenis.css\" data-kid=\"279\">\n<script type=\"module\" data-kid=\"280\">\n  import Lenis from \"https://esm.sh/lenis@1\";\n  const lenis = new Lenis({ autoRaf: true });\n\n  gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);\n\n  // Hero entrance\n  gsap.from('.hero-left', { opacity: 0, y: 40, duration: 1, ease: 'power3.out', delay: 0.2 });\n  gsap.from('.hero-right', { opacity: 0, x: 40, duration: 1, ease: 'power3.out', delay: 0.5 });\n\n  // Stat items\n  gsap.from('.stat-item', {\n    opacity: 0, y: 20, duration: 0.6, stagger: 0.1, ease: 'power2.out',\n    scrollTrigger: { trigger: '.stat-item', start: 'top 85%' }\n  });\n\n  // How it works cards\n  gsap.from('.how-card', {\n    opacity: 0, y: 30, duration: 0.7, stagger: 0.15, ease: 'power3.out',\n    scrollTrigger: { trigger: '.how-card', start: 'top 85%' }\n  });\n\n  // Feature cards\n  gsap.from('.feature-card', {\n    opacity: 0, y: 30, duration: 0.6, stagger: 0.1, ease: 'power3.out',\n    scrollTrigger: { trigger: '.feature-card', start: 'top 85%' }\n  });\n\n  // Testimonials\n  gsap.from('.testimonial-card', {\n    opacity: 0, y: 25, duration: 0.6, stagger: 0.12, ease: 'power3.out',\n    scrollTrigger: { trigger: '.testimonial-card', start: 'top 85%' }\n  });\n</script>\n",
